Hello <%= @user.email %>,

RECIPIENT ADDRESS ADDED

We've added <%= @new_address.name %> to your PostcardMailer address book.

Address Details:
<%= @new_address.address1 %><% if @new_address.address2.present? %>, <%= @new_address.address2 %><% end %>
<%= @new_address.city %>, <%= @new_address.state %> <%= @new_address.postal_code %>

You can now send postcards to this recipient by using their nickname "<%= @new_address.nickname %>" in the "to:" field of your postcard emails.

Example:
To: <%= @new_address.nickname %>@postcardmailer.us
Subject: Greetings from San Francisco!
